1st Approach:- 

LDA 2090H ;Loads the low byte of the number into the accumulator. 
ANI 01H ;ANDs the accumulator with 01H. 
JZ EVEN ;Jumps to EVEN if the result is zero (even number). 
MVI A, FFH ;Loads FFH into the accumulator for an odd number. 
JMP STORE ;Unconditionally jumps to STORE. 
EVEN: 
MVI A, 00H ;Loads 00H for an even number. 
STORE:
STA 20A0H ;Stores the final result in 20A0H. 
HLT

2nd Approach:-
LDA 2090H 
RAR ;Rotate A by 1 bit through CY. D0 goes into CY, old CY goes to D7. 
JNC MVI A, FFH 
JMP STORE 
EVEN: 
MVI A,00H 
STORE: 
STA 20A0H 
HLT
